I do not mean that way!
So I will use my entire being to repay the favor!
I would like you to use me to commute to work again tomorrow!
I had enough of that today.
I was raised to repay all favors, even if owed to foolish, inferior humans!
There is a reason I will not use you to commute.
I think dragons are better left holding down the fort!
You are one of the stronger dragons, right, Tohru?
Strong enough to bring about Armageddon.
It will be a relief to know you are here keeping the house safe.
Well, I am off to the office.

I guess I will ask Fafnir-san.
Kill all who try to steal your treasure.

The person living here is away at this hour.
I did not get to kill them either.
The Strongest Maid in History, Tohru!
There are plenty of other girls you could ask.
You are like one of the guys, though.
I am a maid living with Miss Kobayashi every day.
She is one of my relatives, and I am looking after her.

Would you like to come, too, Tohru-chan?
Wait, are you old enough to drink?
A round after work's the best!

Well, you can drink what you like.
I do not intend to share drinks with you.

Man, still, today's work was rough, was not it?

I told you before, did not I?

First, I use my clairvoyance to check inside your pockets.
Then I separate them into plain and patterned piles,
and wash them using separate detergents.
Then I wash the delicate fabrics by mouth.
I told you, I produce saliva that removes stains.
